A threat actor does not need any specific privileges to potentially exploit this vulnerability. An attacker could perform a man-in-the-middle attack and eavesdrop on encrypted communicati CVE project by @Sn0wAlice

This can lead to privilege escalation. Affected versions are 1.8.0 CVE project by @Sn0wAlice
